### Common Overflow Fixes
- Replace text with icons where possible
- Use tooltips for additional context
- Split complex slides into multiple slides
- Move details to presenter notes
- Use tabs or click-reveals for alternate content

Remember: If content doesn't fit at all screen sizes without forcing tiny text, it's too complex for one slide!